snippet.title: Dencia Interview On The Magazine Show @DaMagazineShow

localized.description:
Songstress and self confessed business woman has been controversy across the globe with her new skin care line whitenyious. She dropped by the BEN TV studios in London for her interview on The Magazine Show with our lovely host Toya A Washington.

(Make sure you check out Toya's beauty channel Youtube Channel: beautybonae)

Twitter @toya_w and @femibentv

 If you wish to feature on The Magazine Show please contact us at magazineshow@ymail.com

You can also find us at:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DaMagazineShow
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/groups/bentvmagazine/
BEN TV: http://bentelevision.com/the-magazine-show/

The award winning Magazine Show airs every Saturday between 1-3pm on Sky Channel 182. See you there!
